keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

" =========================
" Tabs navigation (qutebrowser style)
" =========================
map H previousTab
map L nextTab

" =========================
" History navigation
" =========================
map <c-h> goBack
map <c-l> goForward

" =========================
" Search / Open (space space)
" =========================
map <space><space> Vomnibar.activateInNewTab


" --- Yank / paste links ---
map P openCopiedUrlInNewTab


" =========================
" Link hints
" =========================
map f LinkHints.activateMode
map F LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab

" =========================
" Edit current URL
" =========================
map E Vomnibar.activateEditUrl


" =========================
" open  my github and the atiDocs
" =========================
map <space>mgh createTab https://github.com/MohamedattiaDev
map <space>ati createTab https://mohamedattiaDev.github.io/AtiDocs



unmap x
unmap r
